**Creative Vision:**
- Progressive disclosure UI concept
- Interactive checklist with embedded education
- Multi-project management system
- Template-based scalability architecture

**Strategic Thinking:**
- HTML over app (prioritized accessibility and simplicity)
- Local-first with cloud-ready architecture (privacy + future growth)
- Modular design for easy expansion (FontForge â†’ Canvas â†’ universal)
