**Product Sense:**
- Designed for my actual workflow, not theoretical ideal
- Prioritized features (must-have vs. nice-to-have)
- Planned for multiple audiences (students, designers, educators)
- Thought about distribution and sharing

**Communication:**
- Clearly articulated requirements to technical partner (Claude)
- Asked clarifying questions when confused
- Provided actionable feedback for iteration
- Sought expert review from programmer partner

**Integrity:**
- Proactively insisted on transparent attribution
- Requested verbatim documentation for authenticity
- Distinguished my contributions from AI's
- Advocated for AI collaboration as legitimate methodology

### Claude's Core Contributions

**Technical Education:**
- Explained FontForge concepts (metrics, validation, hinting)
- Clarified technical feasibility of ideas
- Provided implementation options with trade-offs

**Information Organization:**
- Compiled scattered knowledge into structured checklists
- Created comprehensive reference guides
