## Academic Integrity Statement

**This project is a collaboration between a human (me) and an AI (Claude).**

**I take full credit for:**
- Identifying the problem and envisioning the solution
- All creative and strategic decisions
- Product vision and feature ideation
- Requirements specification and prioritization
- Testing, validation, and quality control
- This documentation and reflection

**Claude receives credit for:**
- Technical explanation and education
- Code implementation (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)
- Information compilation and organization
- Documentation formatting and structure

**Why this matters:**
In modern product development, the ability to identify problems, envision solutions, communicate requirements, and collaborate with technical resources is MORE valuable than coding ability alone. This project demonstrates all those skills.

**This is not "cheating" - it's modern collaboration:**
Just as designers work with developers, architects work with engineers, and directors work with cinematographers, I worked with an AI tool to execute my vision. The vision, direction, and decisions are mine.

